entries.transmission_start: Vortex Command: < There's more of them than we can count. I don't know what to tell you pilot, you're in our thoughts, may the force be with you. >
entries.transmission_received: Vortex Command: < You are home free pilot! We are doing the final scans now but it seems the Empire has given up sending more fighters. Amazing job! >
entries.trans_update: Vortex Command: < Keep it up pilot, Our sensor ships are %DI percent done with relocating to a safe location. >
entries.title_d: We may have located a small group of Imperial ships. We will alert you if we find any suitable ships of the Inquisition for you to capture as you head for the waypoints we provide you with.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Disable Imperial ship.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < You're an amazing pilot! Good work. Back to the old objective, try to find and disable a ship of the Imperial Inquisition. >
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: You are at the correct coordinates, stand by while we do a scan for smaller groups of Inquisitor ships.
entries.quest_location_d: You are getting deeper in to Imperial territory and the danger level is increasing, stay alert.
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: You have been spotted! We have multiple Imperial fighters heading your way, prepare for attack!
entries.outofrange_failed: Vortex Command: < You went too deep in to the Imperial territory and they have locked on to you. There's nothing left to do but retreat, return to base! >
entries.outofrange: Vortex Command: < You are getting too far in to Imperial territory, they will lock their capital ships to you! Return to the coordinates we provided you with. >
entries.mission_complete: Mission success! Proceed with further objectives.
entries.found_loc: Proceed to the desginated area. Enemy presence detected.
entries.first_attack: Forget trying to disable ships, they are coming for you en masse! Our sensor ships are close to that location as well so we need you to keep them busy while we relocate.
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.arrived_at_loc: Stay on the alert, pilot. You know the drill. There's enemy activity in these parts. Don't let your guard down.
